stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Plan : runPlan(plan)
    Plan --> Preflight : validate environment
    Preflight --> Harden : Step-2 hardener
    Harden --> Execute : slice loop
    Execute --> Execute : reflexion retry (gate fail)
    Execute --> Sweep : all slices pass
    Sweep --> Execute : completeness gap found
    Sweep --> Review : artifacts consistent
    Review --> Execute : advisory signal (blocking if opted-in)
    Review --> Ship : verdict clean
    Ship --> [*]
    Execute --> Harden : postmortem feeds next hardener
    Review --> Stopped : operator halt
    Stopped --> [*]
